    {
      "chinese": "回想們巴宰人從前有餵奶媽媽互助的故事。昔來自葫蘆墩的巴宰人，經過無數個山頭後遷移到埔里烏牛欄，族人抵達新的土地且每天接觸新的事物，為躲避其他部落人群的殺害並且要守護自家人，每當男人要到外工作時，留下的人都是老幼婦孺！部落頭領總會叮嚀大家要相互團結並互相照顧！",
      "ab": "maxalēkad nohoda Pazeh a saw nita ka hada maabēzēbēdēn ni panunoh inna a pasukuan. pinudah di Hurutul a Pazeh saw ka. minurazaw xanixanisay a binayu liaka patururu di Auran u Poly-sia. Pazeh a sawsaw kadudi xias a daxē iu minasikēla xias a saysay mia’adali. pariuay tahayēn ni ada rētēl a sawsaw iuka maxadēxē’ay talima saw. noka mamalēng usa’ay mukukusa di langu a isia. ngazēbēn a saw ka hakēzēng. rubarubang iu mamais dadua lia! rētēl a taupunu isia rēzaw ka pakwas’i maazēbēzēbay iuka maarapulay dadua.",
